    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-4 font-mono">14. Third-Party Websites</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-2">14.1 Our website includes hyperlinks to other websites owned and operated by third parties; such hyperlinks are not recommendations.</p>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-2">14.2 We have no control over third-party websites and their contents, and we accept no responsibility for them or for any loss or damage that may arise from your use of them.</p>
