    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-2">16.2 The revised terms and conditions shall apply from the date of publication on the website. We will notify registered users of material changes by email.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="border-l-4 border-[var(--color-secondary)] pl-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-4 font-mono">17. Assignment</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-2">17.1 You agree that we may assign, transfer, sub-contract, or otherwise deal with our rights and/or obligations under these terms and conditions.</p>
